{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-less-than-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Poredjenje sa Operatorom Manje Od","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Operator manje od (<code>&#x3C;</code>) poredi vrednosti dva broja. Ako je broj sa leve strane manji od broja sa desne strane, vraca <code>true</code>. U suprotnom vraca <code>false</code>. Kao i operator jednakosti, operator manje od konvertuje tipove podataka pri poredjenju.</p>\n<p><strong>Primeri</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">2   &#x3C; 5 // true\n'3' &#x3C; 7 // true\n5   &#x3C; 5 // false\n3   &#x3C; 2 // false\n'8' &#x3C; 4 // false\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244d6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte operator manje od na oznacene linije kako bi return iskazi imali smisla.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16789,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparison-with-the-less-than-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function testLessThan(val) {\n  if (val) {  // Change this line\n    return \"Under 25\";\n  }\n\n  if (val) {  // Change this line\n    return \"Under 55\";\n  }\n\n  return \"55 or Over\";\n}\n\ntestLessThan(10);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>testLessThan(0)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Under 25</code></p>","testString":"assert(testLessThan(0) === 'Under 25');"},{"text":"<